{"tid":1633864,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[罷食/裝飾] 原來太古城2樓個food court係美心嚟！","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T09:37:53.000Z","uid":85909,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e134953cf7f74ab994b7768d032f5159c73410b5","tid":1633864,"uid":85909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ArAdwx3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FArAdwx3.jpg&h=4cc7de07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太古城2樓有個food court叫 TREATS，有朋友喺嗰度做話我知原來成個food court都係美心嘅！<br />\n<br />\n仲想側側搏唔多覺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就咁上美心官網搵吓已經搵到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/raUayOb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FraUayOb.png&h=5c7c6953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.maxims.com.hk/tc/search/restaurantsearch.asp?id=560&amp;m=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.maxims.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fsearch%2Frestaurantsearch.asp%3Fid%3D560%26m%3D2&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4vhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=aa7518cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.maxims.com.hk/tc/search/restaurantsearch.asp?id=560&amp;m=2</a><br />\n<br />\n再喺Google搵吓 TREATS 美心，就會出現一堆打手文，寫到明：<del>最新登陸太古城的TREATS可能會令你改變對food court的傳統觀念。</del>集美食及生活於一身的<span style=\"color: red;\">TREATS是美心集團</span>其中一個大計劃。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1UOq7cD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1UOq7cD.jpg&h=488fd8fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n各位太古人，你哋識揀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw唔好叫我朋友show證FC，已離職<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bced1ba9b6167c42c5e5d27be0598b9c22fa726a","tid":1633864,"uid":85909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:33:41.000Z","msg":"1/10"}